{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-colon-space-before/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-colon-newline-after/","description":"declaration-colon-space-after Require a single space or disallow whitespace after the colon of declarations. The --fix option on the…","title":"declaration-colon-space-after"},"body":"<h1 id=\"declaration-colon-space-after\"><a href=\"#declaration-colon-space-after\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>declaration-colon-space-after</h1>\n<p>Require a single space or disallow whitespace after the colon of declarations.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**      ↑\n * The space after this colon */</span></code></pre>\n<p>The <code>--fix</code> option on the <a href=\"../../../../user-guide/cli/#autofixing-errors\">command line</a> can automatically fix all of the problems reported by this rule.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#options\">Options</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#always\">\"always\"</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#never\">\"never\"</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#always-single-line\">\"always-single-line\"</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Options</h2>\n<p><code>string</code>: <code>\"always\"|\"never\"|\"always-single-line\"</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"always\"><a href=\"#always\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"always\"</code></h3>\n<p>There <em>must always</em> be a single space after the colon.</p>\n<p>The following patterns are considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color </span>:pink }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>:pink }</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color </span>: pink }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink }</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"never\"><a href=\"#never\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"never\"</code></h3>\n<p>There <em>must never</em> be whitespace after the colon.</p>\n<p>The following patterns are considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>:pink }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color </span>:pink }</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color </span>:pink }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>:pink }</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"always-single-line\"><a href=\"#always-single-line\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"always-single-line\"</code></h3>\n<p>There <em>must always</em> be a single space after the colon <em>if the declaration's value is single-line</em>.</p>\n<p>The following patterns are considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">box-shadow</span>:<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">#5b9dd9</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">rgba</span>(30, 140, 190, 0.8);\n}</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">box-shadow</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">#5b9dd9</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">rgba</span>(30, 140, 190, 0.8);\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">box-shadow</span>:\n    <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">#5b9dd9</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">rgba</span>(30, 140, 190, 0.8);\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">box-shadow</span>:<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">#5b9dd9</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">rgba</span>(30, 140, 190, 0.8);\n}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/declaration-colon-space-after.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-colon-space-after/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-colon-space-after/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-colon-space-after/index.html.ecacb96f8f4e654c36c492a32f74024f.json"}